{"title":"无形广告有偿新闻","authors":["池北偶方成"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":6,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"无形广告有偿新闻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗方成画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"市场经济讲市场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新闻自然该有偿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各行各业要创收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做点交易又何妨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钱给一分货，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出卖版面有商量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想说啥就写啥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也可简短也可长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"费用远比广告省，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"效果倒比广告强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明充当传声筒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却装采访写文章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记者拿钱听使唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既不体面也荒唐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两厢情愿便成交，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"职业道德管他娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传媒甘心降身价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此种歪风岂可长！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}